description: The AfD helped elect liberal Thomas Kemmerich in Thuringia, prompting widespread outrage.
title: Germany AfD: Thuringia PM quits amid fury over far right
title_page: Germany AfD: Thuringia PM quits amid fury over far right - BBC News
maintext: "It was a bad day for democracy, a day that broke with the long and proud tradition of the CDU's values. This is in no way in line with what the CDU thinks, how we have acted throughout our party's existence," she said.
